🧩 4 Sum

Focus:
Pair Sums
Hashing
Complement Matching

Approach:
Store pair sums in a HashMap.
Find complementary sums from remaining pairs.
Count valid combinations efficiently.

Complexity:
Time: O(n²)
Space: O(n²)

🧩 Longest Consecutive Sequence

Focus:
HashSet
Sequence Detection
O(n) Solution

Approach:
Store all numbers in a HashSet.
Start only from numbers without a predecessor.
Expand sequence forward and track maximum length.

Complexity:
Time: O(n)
Space: O(n)

